Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強的殺氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:02:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連呼吸或者轉眼珠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會被人趁隙殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.67,0:02:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方待一個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道會變成什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上忍對決的殺氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺就像生命被掌握在他們手上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.77,0:02:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其這樣 還不如死了痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算死我也會保護你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會讓他殺了我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師後面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水分身術
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以疼痛起誓的決心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒弄清狀況嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單憑隨意的模仿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無法打倒本大爺的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你也不賴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:05:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當時就已經複製了我的水分身術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會讓他殺了我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你故意讓分身說那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的注意力完全吸引到他身上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己卻用霧隱之術躲藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀察著我的一舉一動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是那麼好對付的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙也是假貨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵蒺藜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老師…居然被踢飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他的體術也很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的水似乎很重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水牢術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本打算暫時躲在水裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失算
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你中計了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你絕對無法逃脫的特製牢籠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是讓你自由活動的話 我可不好下手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我待會兒再來收拾你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要先收拾那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水分身術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到他這麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們三個戴上了護額就以為自己是忍者了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些在生死線上徘徊的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等可以登記在本大爺的手冊上時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才有資格被稱為忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你們這種傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒資格稱為忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是普通的小鬼罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快帶著達茲納先生逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們跟他鬥沒有勝算的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我還被困在這個水牢裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就無法離開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水分身只要離開本體一段距離後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之趁現在快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑 不要開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你被困住時起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就別無選擇了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我們現在逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有你的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不斬遲早會追上來殺死我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我們擺出了卍字陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也無法抵禦他的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底我們根本沒有選擇的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了生存下去 我們必須先救出你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能硬拚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助他…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是上忍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得想辦法逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…真的會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以左手的疼痛起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:10:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不會讓別人來救我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會冷靜下來 再也不會逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會輸給佐助呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 把木葉護額送給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在你畢業之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能獨當一面的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 到這邊來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有樣東西想給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個都是沒有資格做忍者的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們面臨的全是玩命的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:10:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及格了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經長大了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是您想像的那個愛惡作劇的小鬼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要超越火影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓全村的人都認同我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經是忍者了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也下定決心不會再次逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋 快退下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 你到底在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人衝過去想幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連佐助都不是他的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你再怎麼拚命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為下忍的我們是絕無勝算的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護額
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊那個沒眉毛的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好趕快在你的手冊上記下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲早會成為木葉忍者火影的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉流忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩渦鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.46,0:13:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看上去比第一次見面時可靠多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個策略
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種狀況下還能談策略
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然還懂得團隊合作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 怎麼會有這種感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人居然會這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要大幹一場了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要大幹一場了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有勝算嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情…情況不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你們快逃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我受困的那一刻起 勝負就已經定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 我們的任務是保護達茲納先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你們忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說這一切都是因我而起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這個時候了 我可不會那麼貪生怕死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 給大家添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就盡情地去戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作好心理準備了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們完全不懂吸取教訓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.58,0:15:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們打算玩忍者遊戲到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在你們這個年紀時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙手早已經沾滿鮮血了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼人再不斬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你也有所耳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一個名叫血霧之裡的霧隱忍者村裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成為忍者有一個最大的難關
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連那種畢業考試都知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種畢業考試
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種畢業考試是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是讓學生互相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來都是吃同一鍋飯的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成兩人一組互相廝殺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到任何一方力竭身亡為止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 本來都是互相幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起建構未來夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此競爭的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好殘忍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年前 霧隱忍者村的畢業考試
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不作出巨大的變革
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為上一年出現一個惡鬼而導致的變革
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變革
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼變革
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個惡鬼到底做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何的猶豫和彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個還沒有取得忍者資格的幼小少年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把當年超過一百人以上的考生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都給殺死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.08,0:18:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且人數還挺多的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不可能打得過他的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要打敗這個傢伙只有這個辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你能想到這個方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風魔手裡劍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影風車
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手裡劍這種東西對我不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.85,0:20:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次你是向著本體來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手裡劍的影子裡還有一把手裡劍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是影手裡劍之術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死角裏還有第二枚手裡劍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 還是太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他躲過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.12,0:22:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 作戰非常成功
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不斬這個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:22:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然完全沒有察覺到我的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:23:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底中了我所設下的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.45,0:23:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是沉著冷靜地判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.77,0:23:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是木葉忍者漩渦鳴人的戰鬥方式哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.76,0:23:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老師 接下來看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.13,0:23:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫輪眼卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你 我還會大顯身手的
